                "text": "A mix couatl casts spells as a 7th-level <a href=\"ClassDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Druid\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\">druid</a>. Druid spells are considered arcane spells for a mix couatl, meaning that it doesn\u2019t need a divine focus to cast them. "
